  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Zambia Land Alliance Work Plan Sep 2009 - Sep 2011. Project provides support to Zambia Land Alliance strategic plan. Objectives: To promote security of customary land and sustainable land use by  poor men, women, and youths, especially in ZLA operational areas. To promote and protect the rights of displaced and potential internally displaced persons and minority groups in ZLA operational areas. To strengthen local accountability in the land administration system for the urban and rural poor in ZLA operational areas. To advocate for appropriate and timely reforms of laws and policies pertaining to land delivery and administration especially for the poor and vulnerable. To provide land related information in innovative and appropriate formats for use by stakeholders at local, national and international levels.</narrative>
  </description>
